import React from "react";
import TableDragSelect from "react-table-drag-select";
import "react-table-drag-select/style.css";
import TimeSlot from './timeslot.js'

export default class Calendar extends React.Component {
  state = {
    cells: [
      [false, false, false, false, false, false],
      [false, false, false, false, false, false],
      [false, false, false, false, false, false],
      [false, false, false, false, false, false],
      [false, false, false, false, false, false],
      [false, false, false, false, false, false],
      [false, false, false, false, false, false]
    ]
  };

  render = () =>
    <TableDragSelect
      value={this.state.cells}
      onChange={cells => this.setState({ cells })}
    >
      <tr>
        <TimeSlot />
        <TimeSlot />
        <TimeSlot />
        <TimeSlot />
        <TimeSlot />
        <TimeSlot />
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <TimeSlot />
        <TimeSlot />
        <TimeSlot />
        <TimeSlot />
        <TimeSlot />
        <TimeSlot />
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <TimeSlot />
        <TimeSlot />
        <TimeSlot />
        <TimeSlot />

        <TimeSlot />
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <TimeSlot />

        <TimeSlot />

        <TimeSlot />
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <TimeSlot />
        <TimeSlot />
        <TimeSlot />
        <TimeSlot />
        <TimeSlot />
        <TimeSlot />
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <TimeSlot />

        <TimeSlot />
        <TimeSlot />

      </tr>
      <tr>
        <TimeSlot />
        <TimeSlot />

        <TimeSlot />
        <TimeSlot />
        <TimeSlot />
      </tr>
    </TableDragSelect>;
}
